            <div class="welovestackoverflow" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <div style="float: left;">
                        <p>
Scope is an enclosing context where values and expressions are associated. Use this tag for questions about different types of scope as well for questions where scope may be unclear.                         </p>
                                            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                            <a title="tag wiki" href="/tags/scope/info">learn more&hellip;</a>
